Kimberly Quinn (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kimberly_Quinn_(actress) 0 Kimberly Pita Quinn is an American actress. She is best known for her role as Gretchen on the FX television series Terriers and for her role as Tess Masterson on the ABC Family series Twisted. She also has made guest appearances on the television series Suddenly Susan, Nash Bridges, Diagnosis: Murder, NYPD Blue, Without a Trace, House M.D., Two and a Half Men and CSI: NY.
